{"tid":2433954,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"S888首載機　小米11下周一襲港","createTime":"2021-03-05T08:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T18:15:44.000Z","uid":52215,"like":8,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f69d2d5c5cf61b35b9fc383a9ee69d48151150","tid":2433954,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrVvmrR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrVvmrR.jpg&h=fce26425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6V0y3Fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6V0y3Fc.jpg&h=4eabedea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小米於今年初發表小米11，由於是全球首款採用Qualcomm Snapdragon 888處理器的智能手機，所以甫發表已引起手機迷關注。事隔兩個多月，廠方終於宣布把此機的國際版本帶來香港，<a href=\"http://並於3月8日晚上8時於官網mi.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%A6%E6%96%BC3%E6%9C%888%E6%97%A5%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A8%E6%99%82%E6%96%BC%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2mi.com&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=bdf1f522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">並於3月8日晚上8時於官網mi.com</a>進行線上發布會，會後仲會即時開訂，一眾米粉咪錯過！<br />\n<br />\n港版小米11又叫Mi 11，內置6.81吋四曲面全面屏、Harman Kardon立體聲雙喇叭、4,600mAH電池、支援Mi Turbo Charge三重快充。鏡頭為108MP 廣角、13MP 超廣角、5MP長焦微距組合，對應光學防震、極黑夜攝、HDR10 +等高階拍攝分唇。國內版有藍、灰2色，現階段未知道港版有哪種顏色，也未知會否引入雷軍簽名版，但可以肯定會有番全Google服務，所以有心入手就不妨等等，勿心急買水買了。"},{"pid":"831e585902e0dcb084425e93f0385a71cf8fb12b","tid":2433954,"uid":653,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"又係你條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cc786e2d1921f6f67c8c7319f70563988be2f6","tid":2433954,"uid":301529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d820fa496f5781306dda020831bed57818080e07","tid":2433954,"uid":173936,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T09:27:28